bdateline":"1620360019","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51168352","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"wuliaozheX","authorid":"389976","dateline":"2021-5-7 12:14","message":"已经放弃了<br />\n换句话说就是真的曾经有过<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/108.png\" /><br />\n到底有多少人想做伞哥哥的laopo啊<br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 HUAWEI TEL-AN00a, Android 10上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.4.4.1","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"25488","username":"wuliaozheX","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"25188","dbdateline":"1620360854","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"51168451","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"gaoxuanl","authorid":"426991","dateline":"2021-5-7 12:21","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=51168201&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">LeonsCat 发表于 2021-5-7 12:00</font></a><br />\n啊啊啊到这段了！！！<br />\r\n伞哥哥你真罪孽深重啊。</div><br />\n然而当初伞哥哥随手一撩的时候又怎能想到会收到一份如此沉重的感情呢<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/001.png\" /><br />\n所以赶紧负起责任入赘吧<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/057.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25489","username":"gaoxuanl","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25189","dbdateline":"1620361319","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51168500","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"ribbon","authorid":"180289","dateline":"2021-5-7 12:26","message":"小肥宅放弃的是等着伞来娶她<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面该是她去娶伞了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/075.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25490","username":"ribbon","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"25190","dbdateline":"1620361614","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"51168512","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"LeonsCat","authorid":"542677","dateline":"2021-5-7 12:27","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=51168352&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">wuliaozheX 发表于 2021-5-7 12:14</font></a><br />\r\n已经放弃了<br />\r\n换句话说就是真的曾经有过<br />\r\n到底有多少人想做伞哥哥的laopo啊</div><br />\n就是伞哥哥太迟钝，没有及时A上去。不然反正参考京都已经通过了同**条例，高中时期就能直接去市役所了。<br />\r\n没关系，现在还来得及，别等到十年后只能在乐器店看小肥宅在电视上吹双簧管。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25491","username":"LeonsCat","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25191","dbdateline":"1620361671","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51168547","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"LeonsCat","authorid":"542677","dateline":"2021-5-7 12:31","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=51168500&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">ribbon 发表于 2021-5-7 12:26</font></a><br />\r\n小肥宅放弃的是等着伞来娶她<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面该是她去娶伞了</div><br />\n从穷小子带着富家女私奔，变成贵妇人包养小鲜肉？","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25492","username":"LeonsCat","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25192","dbdateline":"1620361882","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51168587","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"Eugeo0","authorid":"509951","dateline":"2021-5-7 12:35","message":"阿伞什么时候冲动一把，娶了小肥宅<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/138.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25493","username":"Eugeo0","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"25193","dbdateline":"1620362139","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"51169027","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"gaoxuanl","authorid":"426991","dateline":"2021-5-7 13:15","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\">みぞれが希美を好きなのはみぞれの勝手だし、希美がそれに応える義理なんてない。それに、聡い希美があれだけの重みのある友愛に対して本当に無自覚だとは、夏紀にはとうてい思えなかった。づいていないフリを希美が続けるなら、夏紀だってそれに付き合う。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n霙喜欢希美，是霙的自由，而希美没有必须回应的义务。而且，夏纪觉得希美是这么聪明的的一个人，怎么会完全没意识到呢？尤其在这份友谊是如此沉重的情况下。如果希美继续装作没发现的话，夏纪也只会顺其自然。</div><br />\n与其说伞哥哥迟钝，夏纪倒是觉得伞哥哥明明门清，懂装不懂。<br />\r\n我觉得霙对夏纪说这一番话的重点在于「ただ、一緒にいたかっただけ。でも、それがいちばん難しい。人間は、理由もなく一緒にはいない」<br />\r\n话中话就是：“我跟伞哥哥不在一所大学，找不到在一起的理由了，夏爸爸你别再袖手旁观，多创造点一起玩的机会给我送点助攻啊喂！”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感觉这点可以跟后文比VV和初回特典里骑旋转木马时夏纪对希美说的那些话有所呼应，就是南中四人不能散，夏优要多助攻，伞霙才能往he冲冲冲","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25494","username":"gaoxuanl","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25194","dbdateline":"1620364536","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51169107","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"magicyang1991","authorid":"409448","dateline":"2021-5-7 13:23","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=51169027&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">gaoxuanl 发表于 2021-5-7 13:15</font></a><br />\r\n与其说伞哥哥迟钝，夏纪倒是觉得伞哥哥明明门清，懂装不懂。<br />\r\n我觉得霙对夏纪说这一番话的重点在于「ただ、 ...</div><div class=\"reply_wrap\">&nbsp;  “即使成为大学生了，也想这样四个人一起玩，我是这么想的。”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  右手保持握着把手，夏纪向这边凑近脸。是小孩子做的话会因为危险被父母提醒的姿势。但是，夏纪已经18岁了，希美也已经18岁了。即使昂首挺胸地自称是小孩子，也太过于接近大人了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  “是这样吗？”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  反问的声音自然地变大了。是因为BGM的关系。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  “想去旅游什么的。比如说去鸟取。”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  “啊，话题连接上了。话说不稀奇吗？这种话从夏纪嘴里说出来。”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  基本上这种事的提议者多半是希美和优子。对着歪过头的希美，夏纪不知为何眉头轻皱。欲言又止的嘴，摆出介于苦笑和害羞之间的样子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  “因为刚才对霙说了。”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  “什么？”<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;  “说，四个人再一起出去玩吧。”</div><br />\n所以这不就来了么","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25495","username":"magicyang1991","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"25195","dbdateline":"1620364988","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"51169134","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"gaoxuanl","authorid":"426991","dateline":"2021-5-7 13:25","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=51169107&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">magicyang1991 发表于 2021-5-7 13:23</font></a><br />\n所以这不就来了么</div><br />\n是啊，夏哥哥懂得很<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/057.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25496","username":"gaoxuanl","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25196","dbdateline":"1620365146","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51169483","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"AprilSakura","authorid":"529251","dateline":"2021-5-7 14:08","message":"话说霙为什么要邀请夏纪坐摩天轮呢？<br />\r\n夏纪和霙的对话让我再一次确定了霙的真实性格其实不内向，只是解开封印前太自卑。<br />\r\n其实她心里什么都懂吧，也有很多狡猾的一面。也许霙说不出口喜欢伞哥哥的长笛并不是因为单纯不懂，而是因为她吃长笛的醋所以故意不说。长笛是导致伞哥哥不和她在一起的因素。长笛也好，比赛也好都最讨厌了，所以怎么可能喜欢伞哥哥的长笛。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25497","username":"AprilSakura","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25197","dbdateline":"1620367717","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51169617","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"gaoxuanl","authorid":"426991","dateline":"2021-5-7 14:22","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=51169483&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">AprilSakura 发表于 2021-5-7 14:08</font></a><br />\n话说霙为什么要邀请夏纪坐摩天轮呢？<br />\r\n夏纪和霙的对话让我再一次确定了霙的真实性格其实不内向，只是解开封 ...</div><br />\nフルートの嫁を寝取りしたい令嬢.avi","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25498","username":"gaoxuanl","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25198","dbdateline":"1620368527","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51169628","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"AprilSakura","authorid":"529251","dateline":"2021-5-7 14:23","message":"“在霙的心里，是怎么看希美的？”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“朋友。”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n立即就回答了。毫不犹豫的答案让夏纪有些退缩。<br />\r\n===============================<br />\r\n这段描写很有意思，面对夏纪的这个问题一般来说都要思考一下再回答，尤其是霙对伞哥哥这么沉重复杂的感情。<br />\r\n没想到霙即答。有可能是提前问对这个问题准备好了答案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n“近来的研究发现，说谎所需要的时间会比说实话来得长，因此回答问题所用的时间，可用于测谎[12]；但是，研究也显示立即回答答案可用于“证明”有备而来的谎言。” --摘自**[<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B0%8E%E8%A8%80\">谎言</a>]","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25499","username":"AprilSakura","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"25199","dbdateline":"1620368596","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"51169679","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"cckuku","authorid":"524512","dateline":"2021-5-7 14:28","message":"因为小肥宅已经放弃当伞哥哥的恋人所以才毫不犹豫的说朋友吧<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/138.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"25500","username":"cckuku","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"25200","dbdateline":"1620368901","groupiconid":"10"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":{"51157181":[],"51168028":[],"51168500":[]},"commentcount":{"51157181":null,"51168028":null,"51168500":null},"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"thread-{tid}-{page}-{prevpage}.html","group_group":"group-{fid}-{page}.html","home_space":"space-{user}-{value}.html","home_blog":"blog-{uid}-{blogid}.html","forum_archiver":"{action}-{value}.html","plugin":"{pluginid}-{module}.html"},"setting_rewritestatus":["portal_topic","portal_article","forum_forumdisplay","forum_viewthread","group_group","home_space","home_blog","forum_archiver","plugin"],"forum_threadpay":"","cache_custominfo_postno":["<sup>#</sup>","楼主",""],"forum":{"password":"0"}}}